Neutralization of N501Y #mutant #SARSCoV2 by BNT162b2 (#Pfizer) #vaccine-elicited sera

Sera of 20 participants in a previously reported trial of the mRNA-based #COVID19 vaccine BNT162b2 had equivalent neutralizing titers to the N501 and Y501 viruses.
